          <div class="project-links">
            <a href="/papers/toa-chi26.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-link paper">📄 Paper</a>
            <a href="/videos/toa-demo.mp4" target="_blank" class="btn-link video">▶ Video</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div>
          <h3>NarraSteer：面向数据叙事的 Agent 交互产品设计</h3>
